==English==

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

#(''Australian'') A person who is, or is perceived to be, unsophisticated or of a lower class background, who spends money on flashy or trashy items to fulfil their aspirations of higher social status. The stereotype includes having speech and [[mannerism]]s that are considered to denote poor education and uncultured upbringing, which is reflected in their bad taste possessions and lifestyles. Cashed Up Bogan can be shortened to Cub.

